{"tid":1895914,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［笨撚生物學］ 愛滋病患者係咪唔會中武漢肺炎？","createTime":"2020-02-24T21:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T00:53:44.000Z","uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef7318c3b854c776c973e150b5cd2992dc6ac17","tid":1895914,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T21:49:46.000Z","msg":"愛滋病患者係咪唔會中武漢肺炎？認真問。<br />\n之前有新聞講過愛滋病同武漢肺炎個病毒好相似<br />\n<br />\n假設一個人中左武漢肺炎，佢周圍走只會散播病毒比其他未受感染嘅人<br />\n<br />\n照常理，如果佢遇到另外一個武漢肺炎嘅患者係無得雙重感染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁會唔會有機會愛滋病嘅患者係對武漢肺炎呢種病毒有抗體？有冇相關調查研究過呢件事？定係兩件事無衝突係我自膠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無讀過生物學 純粹FUCK發奇想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好笑鳩我</span>"},{"pid":"81d01c412cfb2bdbd0645602101951c1bc0de153","tid":1895914,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T21:52:31.000Z","msg":"你諗下幾撚多廢老即日來回叫雞都中招武肺"},{"pid":"a1f642a49a7bab3ebb9991797a01fbcf85fcd7c5","tid":1895914,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T21:53:12.000Z","msg":"本身愛滋病會唔會生成抗體<br />\n聽得多都係要食藥維持 好似未聽過可以靠抗體斷藥？"},{"pid":"5615a2bc2a1741841016c1b3fed0983da4f72662","tid":1895914,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1f642a49a7bab3ebb9991797a01fbcf85fcd7c5","tid":1895914,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T21:53:12.000Z","msg":"本身愛滋病會唔會生成抗體<br />\n聽得多都係要食藥維持 好似未聽過可以靠抗體斷藥？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T21:54:04.000Z","msg":"多謝解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d2e50299fce7925658141137d554be169e53f5","tid":1895914,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T22:07:57.000Z","msg":"有人食蝦會過敏，咁食蝦仁會唔會有事"},{"pid":"9ad22602cb561131a12368ef319f7fbe1002da6a","tid":1895914,"uid":68098,"like":0,"d